&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Business, Operations, Finance, Information Systems, Engineering, or a related field preferred, but not required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in asset management, operations, order management, service coordination, or a related function in a high-volume environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing asset lifecycle data, subscriptions, warranties, or service

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
